ic matter\" required for their construction is a negative cosmological\nconstant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 07:24:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2015 13:57:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
