)\na peculiar energy distribution of relativistic electrons. We discuss the first\npossibility in terms of an inhomogeneous helical jet model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 10:22:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-13"}
